OL,3,CLong-standing Guernsey politician to
OL,4,Cstand down at election
OL,6,FOne of longest-serving politicians has
OL,7,Fannounced that he will stand down at
OL,8,Fthe next election.
OL,10,FDeputy Peter Roffey is currently
OL,11,FPresident of the Employment and Social
OL,12,FSecurity Committee and the States'
OL,13,FTrading Supervisory Board.
OL,15,FIn a statement on Monday 27 May,
OL,16,FDeputy Roffey said: "After significant
OL,17,Freflection, I have decided not to
OL,18,Fstand in the 2025 General Election.
