OL,6,F"I have lost none of my innate
OL,7,Finterest in public affairs, nor my
OL,8,Fpassion for the island and the
OL,9,Fcommunity I care so much about.
OL,11,F"Rather my decision is driven by the
OL,12,Ffact that I've been doing politics at
OL,13,Fabsolute full tilt, eyeballs out, for
OL,14,Fthe last eight years."
